{"tid":623843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"甜品突然爆炸　強國女多處燙傷差點毀容！專家：加熱過久所致","createTime":"2018-04-10T10:16:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T13:12:51.000Z","uid":75969,"like":412,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"873f9ad49d0bef5c1905711c40a9f032b13597ca","tid":623843,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:16:19.000Z","msg":"大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n美味的甜點竟然暗藏風險？大陸廣東一名女子近日下班後和朋友相約吃甜點，點了一碗「窩蛋雙皮奶」，正準備品嘗時，雙皮奶竟突然爆炸，造成她臉部、頸部和手臂多處燙傷，目前仍在醫院治療。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/04/10/1314962-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F1314962-XXL.jpg&h=19008ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲甜品突然爆炸，造成女子多處燙傷。（圖／翻攝自微博）</span><br />\n<br />\n據陸媒報導，住在韶關的龍姓女子，2日下班後和朋友去吃甜點，點了一碗窩蛋雙皮奶，想不到卻發生意外，當她用湯匙撈了一口，正準備品嘗時，整碗雙皮奶突然爆炸，造成她多處燙傷。<br />\n<br />\n龍女受傷後，立刻被送往醫院急救，目前仍在醫院治療中。對此，甜品店負責人陳老闆已將雙皮奶下架，指出事故原因是學徒加熱雙皮奶時，「多微波加熱了一分鐘」，原本只要2分鐘就夠了，學徒卻加熱成3分鐘，導致裡面累積過多壓力造成爆炸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=367055\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D367055&d=4NKuUjOPDzp%2FoMqKj1UAQZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=60e63184\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D367055&h=0ec7e06c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=367055</a>"},{"pid":"cf02ae55a01ec65528beb938f7dc567caa052626","tid":623843,"uid":12021,"like":296,"dislike":1,"score":295,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:17:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"231025c7b9f1578ff6098aef7b8137f1b56dc501","tid":623843,"uid":89145,"like":449,"dislike":2,"score":447,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:18:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02e922b41c084ab32197778d142ed58beda73047","tid":623843,"uid":51932,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:18:48.000Z","msg":"有咩唔識爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/