e":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:39:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Superheating\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FSuperheating&d=4NKuUjOPDzp%2FoMqKj1UAQZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=85bad399\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Superheating</a><br />\n中學程度黎<br />\n<br />\n其實微波爐加熱清水都可以爆"},{"pid":"2237847c8b9fcf189d34c6317f86d8a79c851ef7","tid":623843,"uid":41509,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"c64624132a097854dcc83f9654bc593c47ecdbec","tid":623843,"uid":12021,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96869ab6f0679ed7f5b12ee10e2cd1ab6d323de5","tid":623843,"uid":41509,"like":4,"dislike":77,"score":-73,"quote":{"pid":"260c8430a871d9dd8323314a0d41f7e9d4886000","tid":623843,"uid":26156,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:32:27.000Z","msg":"你咪撚on9 啦，你自己試下用微波爐叮燉蛋，睇下會唔會去到個客到爆炸，加熱過左時間，根本個蛋會熟過頭而巢皮，要爆都係廚房爆撚左，點撚樣俾人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 9成又唔知落左咩化學野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:37:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:40:43.000Z","msg":"我個問題咪就係呢到，如果叮兩分鐘係ok ,佢依家叮三分鐘，多左一半時間，根本係會熟過頭而巢皮，我就唔知係咪巢晒皮都照出俾個客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c95addcaad517f584182b78004a225110bf9dda3","tid":623843,"uid":36857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:44:02.000Z","msg":"楊枝甘露都爆炸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cada1df72a4c0ac6fa534d1c261128a1f4a0ece6","tid":623843,"uid":136044,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:44:08.000Z","msg":"Superheating can occur when an undisturbed container of water is heated in a microwave oven. At the time the container is removed, the lack of nucleation sites prevents boiling, leaving the surface calm. However, once the water is disturbed, some of it violently flashes to steam, potentially spraying boiling water out of the container.[3] The boiling can be triggered by jostling the cup, inserting a stirring device, or adding a substance like instant coffee or sugar. The chance of superheating is greater with smooth containers, because scratches or chips can house small pockets of air, which serve as nucleation points. Superheating is more likely after repeated heating and cooling cycles of an undisturbed container, as when a forgotten coffee cup is re-heated without being removed from a microwave oven. This is due to heating cycles releasing dissolved gases such as oxygen and nitrogen from the solvent. There are ways to prevent superheating in a microwave oven, such as putting a popsicle stick in the glass or using a scratched container.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面唔識個D分分鐘有朝一日自己都會爆返次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c299de7e25c86adb04cc4db76892e55d66a5de","tid":623843,"uid":38725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:44:59.000Z","msg":"假架D奶"},{"pid":"da17cbfa6eda01bd112abf4debf19ed918ffd584","tid":623843,"uid":53687,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:48:21.000Z","msg":"厲害了，我的國"},{"pid":"507e9293ae491c6dd3a94d1736f6a88648a07245","tid":623843,"uid":89145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:50:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bdf85a12429d50663619029ca58fb386ee52c241","tid":623843,"uid":51436,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:51:20.000Z","msg":"點解佛跳牆會爆炸嫁？本應foul你出局嫁啦，但見你爆得幾夠卓，仲有少少時間，整過份啦"},{"pid":"f7e05e07bfd6fdf2441a4c1e62529741ff57d7f8","tid":623843,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89dd477d47